\
7x7 board is just an extension of the 6x6 board, with an additional queen in the top left corner or the bottom right corner. It can have a max of 7 queens.\
\
8x8 board can have a max of 8 queens. I used the second approach I had from the 6x6 board. I added two columns in the center so it remained symmetric. Then it was fairly simple to place the queens in the only two possible spots remaining. \
